With.AI/ZAiV/V1/ZAiV-AHP/main.html.title: ZAiV-AHP
With.AI/ZAiV/V1/ZAiV-AHP/main.html.body:
ZAiV-AHP
개요
이것은 ZAiV-AHP에 대한 문서입니다.
ZAiV-AHP는 PCI Interface 버전의 고성능 Edge AI Accelerator 보드입니다.
최대 26 TOPS(Tera-Operations Per Second)의 고성능을 갖춘 Hailo-8™ 엣지 프로세서가 탑재되어 있습니다.
다른 엣지 프로세서에 비해 성능은 높지만 크기가 작고 작동 온도가 낮은 것이  큰 장점입니다.
사양

Processor: Hailo-8™ Edge Processor
Memory: Integreated Memory
TOPS: 26
Input Power: DC 5V/3A
Interfaces
1 x USB Type-C: 5V/3A Power
1 x RJ45(Gigabit Ethernet)
1 x Micro HDMI
2 x USB 2.0
1 x External 5V Fan Connector
1 x Micro 5pin Connector for UART


Operation Temperature: 0℃ ~ 70℃

With.AI/ZAiV/V1/ZAiV-AHP/installation.ht.title: installation
With.AI/ZAiV/V1/ZAiV-AHP/installation.ht.body:
설치
준비

ZAiV-AHP Board
AP Board (Prepare one of the list)
Raspberry Pi CM4
Raxda CM5 (To be supported)


5V/3A USB Type-C Power Adapter
Micro SD Card (32GB or more)
USB Webcam
모니터 (HdMI 지원)
USB 2.0 통합 마우스/키보드 (통합 마우스/키보드가 없는 경우, USB 2.0 허브를 준비합니다.)
케이블류
Micro HDMI to HDMI Cable
Ethernet Cable
USB to Micro 5Pin Cable



외부 인터페이스


Raspberry PI CM4 or Radxa CM5 Modlue Slot
5V/3A Power (USB Type-C Connector)
Micro HDMI
USB 2.0 x 2
Gigabit Ethernet (RJ45)
USB to UART (micro 5pin)
IO Interfaces (2.54mm Pitch 2x20 Header)



External Fan (SMW200-02 Connector)
Pin 1 : 5V
Pin 2 : GND


nRPI BOOT & USB_OTG
Pin 1 : nRPIBOOT (CM4_BOOT)
A low on this pin forces booting from an "RPI server" (PC or another RPi);
if not used, leave floating.
Internally 10K pull up to 3.3V


Pin 2 : USB_OTG_ID (but the correct OS driver also needs to be used.)
Input(3.3V) USB OTG Pin.
Internally pulled up.
When grounded the CM4 becomes a USB host




Micro SD Slot

기본 연결

Raspberry Pi 이미지가 설치된 Micro SD카드를 Micro SD카드 슬롯에 삽입합니다.
모니터의 전원을 연결하고 모니터와 ZAiV-AHP간에 micro HDMI to HDMI 케이블을 연결합니다.
USB 키보드/마우스를 연결합니다.
인터넷이 가능한 Etherent Cable을 RJ45 포트에 연결합니다.
USB Webcam을 연결합니다.
UART를 통한 디버깅이 필요한 경우, Micro USB 케이블을 연결합니다.
마지막으로 USB Type-C Power Adapter를 연결합니다.

With.AI/ZAiV/V1/ZAiV-AHU/main.html.title: ZAiV-AHU
With.AI/ZAiV/V1/ZAiV-AHU/main.html.body:
ZAiV-AHU
Overview
This is the documentation for ZAiV-AHU.
ZAiV-AHU is an Edge AI Accelerator board with high performance.
It is equipped with the Hailo-8™ Edge Processor with high performance of up to 26 TOPS (Tera-Operations Per Second).
It has high performance compared to other edge processors, but it is characterized by a small size and low operating temperature.
In addition, it is composed of USB interface and can support from PC to embedded boards such as RaspberryPi and i.MX.
In particular, it is manufactured in a size optimized for Raspberry PI, and has many advantages in miniaturization and light weight.
Specifications

Processor: Hailo-8™ Edge Processor
Memory: Integreated Memory
TOPS: 26
Input Power: DC 5V/3A
Connectivity
USB Type-C
Power & Data(USB3.2 Gen1 x1 (5Gbps))
Auxiliary Power




Operation Temperature: 0℃ ~ 70℃

Physical Specification

With.AI/ZAiV/V1/ZAiV-MHC/main.html.title: ZAiV-MHC
With.AI/ZAiV/V1/ZAiV-MHC/main.html.body:
ZAiV-MHC
Overview

This is the documentation for ZAiV-MHC.
ZAiV-MHC is a vision system that can be applied to various fields through its outstanding AI system and high-performance camera module.
In particular, the size of the camera and AI module is very small while maintaining high performance targeting edge devices.
By separating the camera and module, you can easily install it wherever you want.
Specifications

System Module
NXP i.MX8M Application Processor
4x Cortex-A53 up to 1.8 GHz
Cortex-M7 up to 800 MHz
32-bit DDR4 and LPDDR4 up to 4.0GT/s
1 x MIPI CSI
Video Decode: 1080p60, h.265/4, VP9, VP8
Video Encode: 1080p60, h.265/4
GPU: 16 GFLOPS (high-precision) OpenGL® ES 3.1/3.0, Vulkan®, Open CL™ 1.2 FP, OpenVG™ 1.1


Hailo 8 AI Processor
Unprecedented AI compute power of 26 Tera-Operations Per Second (TOPS)
Best-in-class power efficiency with typical power consumption of 2.5W
Enabling real-time, low latency & high-efficiency AI inferencing on edge devices


Interfaces
1x Gigabit Ethernet (Supported POE)
1x USB Type-C (USB 2.0)
Extention IO
Digital Input: 4ea (24V NPN Isolated)
Digital Output: 4ea (24V NPN Isolated)
UART Console: 1ea
PWM (For Light Brightness Control)






Camera
MIPI Interface
13MP Color
Sensor : 1/3.2" Optical format CMOS Image sensor
Pixel size : 1.1μm x 1.1μm
Focus Type : Auto focus
Focus Distance : 100mm to Infinity
Sensor Active Area: 4208(H) x 3120(V)
Resolution : 640x480(1200fps), 1280x720(80fps), 1920x1080(60fps), 3840x2160(15fps), 4192x3120(10fps)
Temperature : -30 ~ 70 °C
Shutter Type : Rolling Shutter
FOV: 74.4°(D), 60.2°(H), 46.4°(V)
Cable Length : 1m
